My Daily Lifestyle

The project aims to develop a Health Check Report extension for the existing platform, MyDailyLifestyle.com. The extension will enable adding health check data to a dossier and generate a comprehensive report that will be sent via email to the participant. This extension seeks to enhance the overall health check process by providing a streamlined and efficient way to record, analyze, and share health check data.

About

Brand: My Daily Lifestyle

Location: Maarssen, Netherland

Industry: Healthcare

Budget:: $10,000 – $49,000

Clutch Review: 

5.0
 5/5

Product link: mydailylifestyle.com 

Type of software: Web App

Scope of work: Back-end, Front-end, Refactoring, Quality Assurance

My Daily Lifestyle enables adding health check data to a dossier and generates a comprehensive report that will be sent via email to the participant. This extension seeks to enhance the overall health check process by providing a streamlined and efficient way to record, analyze, and share health check data.

Technologies

Ruby on rails

Core-js

jQuery

What our client
wanted

Angela Champness

General Manager, MyDailyLifestyle

We needed to make a Health Check Report extension to improve the efficiency of the health check process within the MyDailyLifestyle.com platform. The existing system lacks a dedicated feature to capture, analyze, and share health check data, resulting in manual and fragmented processes

Challenge

  • There was a challenge for coaches in managing participant health information and hinders effective communication between coaches and participants. The business need is to streamline these processes, enhance data analysis capabilities, and facilitate meaningful discussions around health check results.

Key features

  • Streamline the health check process for coaches, reducing manual efforts and administrative burdens.
  • Enhance participant engagement by providing comprehensive and visually appealing health check reports.
  • Improve communication between coaches and participants, fostering meaningful discussions and goal-setting.
  • Optimize data analysis capabilities for coaches, enabling data-driven decisions and personalized interventions.
  • Enhance efficiency and productivity for coaches, freeing up time for valuable interactions with participants.
  • Ensure the confidentiality and security of participant health check data.
  • Drive user adoption and satisfaction by providing a comprehensive and user-friendly health management solution.
  • Establish a competitive advantage in the health and wellness industry through enhanced functionality and differentiated features.

Project Team

Inna

Project Manager​

Project Manager

Fullstack developer

Yurii

Client’s review

Angela Champness

General Manager, MyDailyLifestyle

Overall experience was very positive. The QT Global team (developer, project manager and tester) were commited and engaged in the project. The development went very well and met the specification. Also spent extra time researching legacy issues with the platform that complicated the work. The team also persisted with various bug fixed post release. Overall very pleased.

5.0
 5/5

Business Value

We have created an extension that reduces manual labor and fully automates the process of filling out and managing data

Fully tested and deployed Health Check Report extension;
